Dirty Word Configuration Tool

- Open 'index.html' in any web browser to start configuration.
- Once 'index.html' is open, follow direction on screen.


Version: 0.01 - Initial Scripting.  
Version: 0.02 - Based on feedback from Aaron have added escape sequence for '//'.  
				Changed '//' to appear as '\/\/' for regular expression engine to parse correctly.
Version: 0.03 - Added functionality to input vdom based on the fact all vdom's maintain their 
 				own dirty 'xmpp' dirty word list.  Also changed the starting integer to 1 because fortigate is not zero based index for dirty words.
				